transcript:

Executive: Hello

Customer: Haan boliye. Dhanshi, aur main Surmila baat kar rahi hun Ganesh agency se.

Executive: Haan.

Executive: Urmila mam very good afternoon. Main Reshu baat kar rahi hun IndiaMART Noida office se.

Executive: Ji ji. Mam actually abhi aapki na Amit se ek video meeting hui thi hai na. Aur us video meeting pe aapne abhi feedback mein no share kiya hai mam. To wohi jaanna chah rahi thi mam kahan pe problem aa gaya tha matlab meeting ke dauran aisi kya cheez rahi.

Executive: Mam abhi jo video aapke paas kya mam?

Customer: Haan.

Executive: Us google meeting ka ek feedback gaya tha mam aapko aapne usse no share kiya hai not satisfied. To main wohi jaanna chah rahi hun ki mam meeting pe aisa kya point kahan pe ho?

Customer: Kahan pe ho?

Executive: Mam woh whatsapp pe jata hai na aapke feedback ke liye to aapne us pe no share kiya hai. To wohi mujhe jaanna tha ki matlab kya reason tha mam.

Customer: Whatsapp pe kiya hai kya maine?

Executive: Ji.

Customer: Ek minute mujhe check karne do. Kya kiya hai woh.

Customer: Kahan pe jaana hai mujhe abhi whatsapp pe?

Executive: Mam aapko ek feedback ka message aaya hoga na video meeting ke baad aapko feedback ka ek message aaya hoga.

Customer: Whatsapp se boliye ki jahan se hmm aur aap apna mail check kariye mam ek baar mail mail pe check kariye aapne jis mail se join kiya tha wahan pe ek baar check karo aapko ek feedback aaya hoga na meeting ka.

Customer: Ek minute.

Customer: Reshu dot Yadav yahi hai na isme?

Executive: Mam woh aapko ek feedback aaya hoga ki you have recently interacted with Amit and are you satisfied with the meeting is tarike se aapne not satisfied kiya hai wahan pe aapko yahan pe nahi gayi na mam ne.

Customer: Ji.

Customer: Yahan pe maine touch nahi kiya hai na sir sir ne mujhe link bheja tha na.

Executive: Mam woh nahi aapne meeting ke baad ek feedback aaya hoga aapko feedback aaya hoga wohi puch rahi main aapko kahan pe aaya hai.

Executive: Mail pe mam aapke registered mail pe aaya hoga to mail se aapne feedback pata nahi hai kaun sa email id se aaya hai mujhe.

Executive: Ek baar main check karti hun mam rukiye.

Executive: Mam aisa to nahi hai ki aapki jagah sir ne kar diya ho aisa to nahi hai aisa to nahi hai sir ne feedback no share kiya ho meeting aapke sath hui thi aur sir ne share kiya ho no aisa kyunki register mail id to sir ka hai na wo to maine padha bhi nahi hai aap boli na to abhi ye kiya maine idhar idhar aaya fail to complete site audit ye kuch hai kya?

Executive: Kya aa raha hai mam kya likh ke aa raha hai?

Customer: Subject hai milk ocean dot in fail to complete site audit ye hai kya?

Executive: Nahi nahi mam woh feedback ke naam se aa raha hoga.

Customer: Yahan pe subject bhi nahi hai milk ocean in fail to complete site audit dusra aa raha hai happening now reshu dot yadav ye subject aa raha hai.

Customer: Hello.

Executive: Mam dekho abhi ye jo aapki video meeting hui hai na aapki hui hai Amit ke sath theek hai uske baad aapne feedback share aaya hai ki aapne matlab not satisfied ka feedback maine kuch matlab feedback fill nahi kiya hai mam.

Executive: Achcha aapne nahi kiya to mam aisa to nahi hai sir ne kar diya ho whatsapp se kiya hai mam maine whatsapp pe kiya hai wo register number to mam sir ka hi hai na to sir sir pe sir ke paas gaya hoga unhone no share kiya hai shayad meeting aapne ki hai aur mam sir ne no share kiya hai aap ek baar mam sir se baat karke boliye na kyunki meeting mein aapko kya issue reh gaya maine to aapko isi
